nodes.label: message
nodes.text: I have had pain on the left side of my breast and right above in the chest area. I also have what feels like muscle pain in my shoulder blade area and my upper arm. I think it may be a pulled muscle? Is there anything I can get to help with that pain? I have tried ibuprofen and I tried Gabapentin this morning, but the pain is still there and is really affecting my days. I also feel a little tingling in my upper arm at times. Could you give  me some suggestions or let me know if there is anything I can take to help this? It has been going on for about 4 days now. Thanks,  Person1
